The SUPERCASA app, the national real estate portal, is a new way to search for the house you dream of, sell your house and interact with real estate agents or owners who advertise their properties here.

Developed by Janela Digital, a technology leader for the real estate sector, the app is based on the vast knowledge of the experience of looking for a property online to provide you with a super useful, unique and free service, whether you are looking for a house or apartment to live in, a bedroom for rent, a farm in the countryside or a shop, office or warehouse for your company.

Know the incredible experience that the SUPERCASA app can provide you:

When searching for houses (and other types of properties):

- Type of business (buy / rent) or specific characteristics of a house (eg Swimming pool)
- Certain point of interest or popular place, writing only its name in the search box (ex: Castelo Óbidos);
- In the vicinity of where you are, using the “Near me” feature;
- Using results in a listing or identifying possible choices on a map;
- Valuing good photos and multimedia elements (videos)

In the interaction with mediators or private owners:

- Through simple forms that notify the advertiser;
- In the possibility of connecting directly;
- When searching for brokers to whom you want to entrust the sale of your property;

Adapting to your case and your time availability:

- Keeping the last searches you've done, to return to them whenever you want;
- Saving your favorite properties or the last ones you've seen in detail;
- Choosing the foreign language you might need;
- Setting notifications to be notified of the entry of new properties;
- Allowing you to put your house up for sale or for rent;

Install the SUPERCASA app now and share your experience with everyone. It's super easy. You create your SUPERCASA profile and access it via your email or your account (profile) on Google, Facebook or Apple.

Your opinion is very important to us. Help us to improve further the service or praise our team of developers and analysts.
